race.comment: DASHING SERPENT (1) found traffic in the run and collided, missing the frame when a 5 length seventh (17.76) at this track in a Grade 6. Has the ability and can bounce back. GRANDAD KEVIN (2) found traffic in the run and collided, missing the frame when a 4.5 lengths fifth (17.73) at this track in a Grade 6. Key chance on best form. CUPID'S DREAM (5) has been out of the placings at his last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (17.80) in a Grade 5 at this track. Can hit the frame this time. CHAROS ROYAL (3) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.
